reviews: I want one. Bought as gift and they love it! Only problem is my bed is a King so I can’t order this one for me-too small and that is only where it loses a 1/2 mark!

review_title: Doesn't work and don't like the scent.
reviews: I am not interested in giving a poor review. But I don't like to waste money and in this case I did, with two purchases. Wet feel, didn't work even after a few applications in the day ..and it smells. I do not like scent especially on me. I imagined Aloe smelling more natural. Led me to continue the search for the right product.

Smells great but that is it. Doesn't work for myself or pre-teen. Even after applying a few times in the day. Also has a slightly more wet feel than preferred. Bought another scent too so wasted money.
